name: The Washbag
description:
Every traveller needs a carry along bag to store their toiletries. Why not get one that is not only sturdy but also waterproof!  This washbag is made using 100% lightweight cotton canvas that is not only waterproof but sturdy. A reinforced base means that this bag will remain flat on  any surface.

A thick leather hand loop allows for portability and hanging. A fully waterproof interior is completed with fine leather detailing. A large external detailed zipper completes this bag. Total travel chic!

Dimensions: L 9.8″ x W 4.3″ x H 5.5″ Weight: 0.4 Kg/0.88 lbs

name: The Tablet
description:
Secure your tablet with this wonderfully sturdy case. Comprised of brown pull-up leather with fine nappa leather detailing, this tablet case features reinforced front and back covers protecting your tablet from harm.

The inner of each cover is lined with 100% nappa leather providing a chic finish. An adjustable elastic fastener and corner grooves secure your tablet in place, while a pen loop and slot pockets provide additional function to this case.

Dimensions: : L 10.2″ x W 7.8″xD 0.5″    Weight:0.4Kg/0.88 lbs

name: The Everyday
description:
A briefcase for your daily needs! This briefcase is made entirely out of brown nappa leather, tanned with only the finest dyes. External combined buckles allow for quick release and fastening of two lined external pockets. An internally lined divider allows for a separation of the inner barrel separating your laptop and files. Two internal, lined, zipper pockets provide even more storage, adding further purpose to this already multifunctional piece.

The bag features a distinct stitching pattern with light red thread adding a distinct flair to this item. This stitching is continued on the sturdy handles and optional shoulder strap.

Dimensions: L 16.1″ x W 5.9″ x H 12.0″   Weight: 1.5Kg/3.3 lbs

name: The Weekender
description:
An instant classic! This tan weekender tote is comprised of 100% Kenyan tan pull-up leather. The treatment of the leather with this method allows for a supple feel and distinct look. This leather will age well, darkening over time to give a distinguished look.

The bag features sturdy carrying handles that are adjustable for length. An external shoulder strap is included for alternative carrying options. A completely lined inner barrel gives the bag a lavish finish  while the addition of a fully lined inner zipper pocket provides for extra storage. Two line external pockets are also available for additional use on the go.

Dimensions: L 19.7″ x W 9.4″ x H 12.6″  Weight: 1.5Kg/1.3 lbs

name: The Shopper
description:
Perfectly sized and perfectly coloured, these great shoppers make for a wonderful addition to your daily wardrobe. Specifically designed using a lightweight, waterproof, 100%cotton canvas  these bags feature a deep inner barrel allowing you to fit all your daily needs.

A fully lined inner compartment is complete with a fully lined inner zipper pocket for more storage. A reinforced leather base gives this bag a strong foundation, while the thicker canvas gives the bag its structure. Sturdy carrying handles mean that this bag is strong enough to carry you through the day.

Dimensions: L 9″ x W 5.9″ H 10.6″   Weight:0.5Kg/1.1 lbs
